  Given a sober space <fr:tex>X</fr:tex>, the subsets of of <fr:tex>X</fr:tex> that are sober as subspaces
  are exactly its <fr:link
href="axt-004R.xml"
type="local"
addr="axt-004R">Skula</fr:link>-closed subsets.
